title: Hiker Told Her Mother ‘I’m Not Afraid of Much’ in Final Text Before Falling from Volcano
description: Juliana Marins' body was found on June 24, days after falling while hiking in Indonesia
content:
A 26-year-old woman's final text message to her mom before she died after falling from a volcano while hiking has been revealed.
